## Project Structure

```text
mcp-json-yaml-toml/
├── packages/mcp_json_yaml_toml/  # Core logic
│   ├── server.py                 # MCP implementation
│   ├── yq_wrapper.py             # Binary management
│   ├── schemas.py                # Schema validation
├── .github/                      # CI/CD and assets
├── docs/                         # Documentation
└── pyproject.toml                # Project config
```

